': ..., '_source': 'nous'} on success, indicating integration with Nous API"],"files":["server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9tehqa_f66321bcd9fa","importance":3,"narrative":"A timeout value in the HTTP request handler was increased to accommodate slower API response times. This is a resilience improvement for external API calls, reducing the likelihood of timeout errors when the Nous endpoint takes longer than 30 seconds to respond.","sessionId":"ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf","subtitle":"Adjusted urllib.request.urlopen timeout in server.py","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:51:53.788Z","title":"Increase API request timeout from 30s to 120s","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mr9tesek_39282815aaea":{"concepts":["model configuration","reasoning content filtering","GLM-5.2","timeout configuration"],"confidence":1,"facts":["api/index.py line 2310: \"max_tokens\": 8000","api/index.py line 2323: urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=120)","api/index.py lines 2165/2191/2364-2365: reasoning content removal functions for GLM-5.2","server.py line 2104: \"max_tokens\": 8000","server.py line 2117: urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=120)","server.py lines 1956/1984: reasoning content removal docstrings"],"files":["api/index.py","server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9tesek_39282815aaea","importance":3,"narrative":"The grep command verified that configuration changes were symmetrically applied across both api/index.py and server.py. The confirmation shows max_tokens set to 8000, HTTP timeouts at 120 seconds, and reasoning content filtering logic (including GLM-5.2 specific handling) present in both files.","sessionId":"ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf","subtitle":"Grep to confirm max_tokens=8000, timeout=120, and reasoning content filtering","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:07.624Z","title":"Verify applied config changes in api/index.py and server.py","type":"search"},"obs_mr9texx4_2f8f0b841f74":{"concepts":["OpenCode API integration","Bearer token authentication","Environment variable configuration"],"confidence":1,"facts":["